    "English": "A map showing the location of a nearby planetary settlement, acquired from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Space Station Cartographer</span>.<br><br>Select the map and use <VAL_ON>Plot Route (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> to pin the location in your Exosuit display.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "显示附近行星定居点的地图，可在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">空间站的制图师处获得</span>。<br><br>选择地图并使用<VAL_ON>规划路线（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）<>以在你的套装屏幕中标记该地点。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "顯示附近星球聚居地位置的地圖，從<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空站地圖學家</span>的手中取得。<br><br>選取地圖，並使用<VAL_ON>規劃路線功能 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<>，即可在你的強化套裝顯示器中釘選該地點。"
  },
